snippet.title: Ninja Prophecy - Part 1: First 1 hour of gameplay (2022 Remake, No Commentary)
snippet.description:
Now that I've figured it out in order to play Java games in KEmulator with the post-1800s versions of Windows 10, you'll need to download and install Java Runtime Environment before you can play with stable performance.
JRE: http://www.java.com/en/download/index.jsp
